headline: T-Mobile adds free new service as it loses phone customers
summary: Amid an increasingly competitive wireless market, T-Mobile has doubled down on launching new offers, such as iPhone deals and free phone lines, to retain loyal customers. Despite these efforts, the carrier continues to see more of its phone customers switch to other providers. As it battles ...
